OL,3,CCare sector has seen too many empty
OL,4,Cpromises
OL,6,FFrom what I'm picking up, the care
OL,7,Fsector is broadly welcoming of the
OL,8,Fgovernment's new tweaks to the sector
OL,9,Fin England (and they are only
OL,10,F'tweaks'), as well as the longer term
OL,11,Fcommission which promises more
OL,12,Fsignificant reform.
OL,14,FBut after two previous government
OL,15,Fcommissions, one government review,
OL,16,Fthree independent commissions, five
OL,17,Fwhite papers and 14 parliamentary
OL,18,Fcommittee inquiries... you can
OL,19,Funderstand why they also feel
OL,20,Fsceptical.
