OL,3,CCare sector has seen too many empty
OL,4,Cpromises
OL,6,FThe timeline of the commission means
OL,7,Fthat the final report will be
OL,8,Fdelivered by 2028 - shortly before the
OL,9,Fnext (anticipated) election.
OL,11,FThis fits with what the prime minister
OL,12,Ftold me on the ITV Tonight programme
OL,13,Fduring the election campaign in June -
OL,14,Freform will be for the next parliament.
OL,16,FFor a sector that's already been
OL,17,Fthrough hell during the pandemic and
OL,18,Fheard countless promises of reform
OL,19,Fsince the late 1990s, waiting another
OL,20,Fthree years is quite some ask.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
