OL,4,Cpromises
OL,6,FThe care sector would much rather skip
OL,7,Fstraight to reform now.
OL,9,FIn terms of the more immediate
OL,10,F'tweaks' to the sector, some extra
OL,11,Ffunding (in the tens of millions) is
OL,12,Fwelcome, but the reforms ask more of
OL,13,Fthe care sector for effectively the
OL,14,Fsame overall money.
