OL,3,CCare sector has seen too many empty
OL,4,Cpromises
OL,6,FIndeed, the government's own press
OL,7,Frelease says the changes are designed
OL,8,Fto relieve pressure on the NHS. So,
OL,9,Fnot specifically about helping the
OL,10,Fsocial care sector itself then?
OL,11,FNothing irks care providers more than
OL,12,Fwhen they play second fiddle to the
OL,13,Fhealth service, as we saw during the
OL,14,Fpandemic.
OL,16,FAs one care organisation gravely put
OL,17,Fit, "The social care sector is on its
OL,18,Flast legs. Without urgent action,
OL,19,Fthere will be nothing left to reform."
